o-by-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Barry-Keoghan-Photo-by-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Barry-Keoghan-Photo-by-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Barry-Keoghan-Photo-by-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan) 加入了即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders"><em>《浴血黑帮》</em></a>电影的演员阵容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-interviews/steven-knight-this-town-peaky-blinders-cillian-murphy-3750204">史蒂文·奈特谈<em>《这个小镇》</em>和他的大预算电影<em>《浴血黑帮》</em></a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>今天（8 月 29 日）确认，这位演员（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/saltburn"><em>《索尔特伯恩》</em></a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-banshees-of-inisherin-review-colin-farrell-brendan-gleeson-3333646"><em>《伊尼舍林女妖》</em></a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-batman"><em>《蝙蝠侠</em></a>》）将与 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/cillian-murphy-confirmed-return-peaky-blinders-movie-3607379">希里安·墨菲</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/rebecca-ferguson-joins-cillian-murphy-in-peaky-blinders-movie-3778325">丽贝卡·弗格森</a>一起出现在这部新电影中。</p><p>目前尚不清楚基奥根将扮演什么角色。请查看下面的官方公告。</p><p>这部即将上映的电影被描述为“屡获殊荣的黑帮传奇的史诗般的延续”，由<em>《浴血黑帮》的</em>创作者兼编剧史蒂文·奈特执笔。该剧将由汤姆·哈珀执导，他执导了该剧第一季的几集。</p><p>奈特在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-interviews/steven-knight-this-town-peaky-blinders-cillian-murphy-3750204">今年 4 月接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>透露， <em>《浴血黑帮》</em>电影的拍摄将于 9 月开始。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan) 已加入即将上映的《浴血黑帮》电影的演员阵容，另外还有此前宣布的希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 和丽贝卡·弗格森 (Rebecca Ferguson)！ <a href="https://t.co/1vrmn98D93">pic.twitter.com/1vrmn98D93</a></p><p> - Netflix (@netflix) <a href="https://twitter.com/netflix/status/1829149527020044631?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 29 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他解释说：“我只是在做最后的润色，这将持续到我们开始拍摄的前一天。但我们就在那里。我们已经把一切都安排好了，我们已经得到了我们需要的所有承诺，我们已经准备好了。”</p><p>至于粉丝们对这部长片项目的期望，奈特告诉<em>NME</em> ：“我认为这部电影将再次向前迈进， <em>Peaky 的</em>粉丝们可以在一个地方见面并观看它，这真是太棒了。</p><p> “预算将会更大，但也因为我们知道我们即将结束这一章，所以我们都会尽力做到最好。希里安（墨菲）真的很愿意。所以我已经等不及要开始拍摄了。”</p><p>墨菲在 6 月份接受<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/06/peaky-blinders-movie-netflix-cillian-murphy-1235958745/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a>采访时表示：“汤米·谢尔比似乎还没有结束我的生活。很高兴能与史蒂文·奈特和汤姆·哈珀在电影版<em>《浴血黑帮</em>》中重新合作。这是为球迷准备的。”</p><p>这部尚未上映的电影的情节细节目前仍处于严格保密状态。尚未确认其他演员。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-recaps/peaky-blinders-season-6-finale-recap-3196803"><em>《浴血黑帮》</em>第六季也是最后一季</a>将于 2022 年在 BBC One 播出。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barry-keoghan-joins-cast-of-new-peaky-blinders-film-3788832">巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan) 加入新电影《巅峰黑帮》(Peaky Blinders) 的演员阵容</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
聆听 Manic Street Preachers 的胜利新单曲“Decline & Fall” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-manic-street-preachers-triumphant-new-single-decline-fall-3788823?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-manic-street-传教士凯旋新单衰落Andrew TrendellThu, 29 Aug 2024 16:02:39 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3788823 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="躁狂街传教士，2024 年。图片来源：Alex Lake" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>听听受 Skids 和 Cardigans 影响的新歌曲，这首歌曲“庆祝在接受和拥抱有控制的衰退的同时仍然存在的微小奇迹”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-manic-street-preachers-triumphant-new-single-decline-fall-3788823">聆听 Manic Street Preachers 的胜利新单曲《Decline &amp; Fall》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="躁狂街传教士，2024 年。图片来源：Alex Lake" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/manic-street-preachers">Manic Street Preachers</a>带着他们成功的新单曲“Decline &amp; Fall”回归。看看下面。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="468" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/manic-street-preachers-ultra-vivid-lament-nicky-wire-james-dean-bradfield-3020202"><b>躁狂街传教士接受采访：“我们通过遗忘来谈论自己”</b></a></li></ul><p>这首歌<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-tease-new-material-so-much-for-the-decline-fall-3787472">整周都在被调侃</a>，这首歌是在乐队 1994 年开创性专辑《The Holy Bible》30 周年纪念日前夕发布的，也是他们自 2021 年广受好评的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-score-first-uk-number-one-album-in-23-years-with-the-ultra-vivid-lament-3048680">排行榜冠军</a>第 14 张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/manic-street-preachers-the-ultra-vivid-lament-review-3035938">《The Ultra Vivid Lament》</a>以来的第一首新作品。</p><p>这首单曲采用了他们之前唱片中一些复古未来主义的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA</a>风格的声音，并与《Resistance Is Futile》和《Everything Must Go》的竞技场欢快声相遇，但受到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-skids">The Skids</a>和《Gran Turismo》中 Manics 的影响而向前发展。 &#39;时代的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-CARDIGANS">羊毛衫</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-war-on-drugs">毒品战争</a>。</p><p> “在音乐上，我们试图通过‘Decline &amp; Fall’创造前进的动力——一首利用过去将其推向未来的歌曲——歌词是一种认识和理解——庆祝仍然存在的微小奇迹，同时接受和拥抱管理“衰落”，“Decline &amp; Fall”乐队说道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Manic Street Preachers - 衰落与堕落（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/viRpkxdBDWA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首歌是在乐队位于纽波特的 Door To The River 工作室和蒙茅斯传奇的 Rockfield Studios 录制的，由定期合作者 Dave Eringa 和 Loz Williams 制作，并由 Caesar Edmunds（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BEACH-HOUSE">Beach House</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/SUEDE">Suede</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">Wet Leg</a> ）混音。</p><p>乐队在 6 月接受<a href="https://www.loudersound.com/features/nicky-wire-tour-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Louder Sound</i></a>采访时讨论了他们即将推出的第 15 张专辑，当时他们称这张专辑“已完成 90%”，并可能于 2025 年 1 月或 2 月发行。</p><p> “它有很大的能量，尽管我感觉不是特别有活力，”贝斯手兼作词家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/NICKY-WIRE">Nicky Wire</a>说。 “其中一首歌曲像是我们最喜欢的两个乐队 The Cardigans 和 The Skids 的混合体，另一首听起来像是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/DINOSAUR-JR">Dinosaur Jr</a>演奏的《Come Up And See Me》（由 Steve Harley 和 Cockney Rebel 演唱）。” </p><figure id="attachment_3788827" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3788827" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3788827" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1.jpg" alt="躁狂街传教士，2024 年。图片来源：Alex Lake" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3788827" class="wp-caption-text">躁狂街传教士，2024 年。图片来源：Alex Lake</figcaption></figure><p>这位威尔士偶像和前 NME Godlike Genius 获奖者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-share-unreleased-song-rosebud-from-new-know-your-enemy-reissue-3274690">于 2022 年发行了专辑《Know Your Enemy》</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-announce-20th-anniversary-re-issue-of-lifeblood-3583696">于今年早些时候发行了《Lifeblood》</a> ，而去年 Nicky Wire <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manics-nicky-wire-surprise-releases-new-solo-album-intimism-3464073">出人意料地发行了他的第二张个人专辑《Intimism》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-nicky-wire-announces-new-art-exhibition-in-wales-3778384">Wire 目前正在彭布罗克郡的纳贝斯博物馆举办一场<i>名为“我的小帝国”</i>的艺术展，展览将持续到 12 月</a>，其中展出了 26 件作品，展示了他对宝丽来照片的喜爱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="躁狂街传教士访谈：关于“抵抗是徒劳的”、生存以及他们的未来" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/y-S8ACSuMeM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>乐队还计划于明天（8 月 30 日）一次性放映音乐会电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-unveil-first-clip-of-new-film-be-pure-be-vigilant-behave-1555173"><i>《BePure-BeVigilant-Behave</i></a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-to-celebrate-30th-anniversary-of-the-holy-bible-with-special-film-screening-3765943">》，以庆祝其 1994 年专辑《The Holy Bible》发行 30 周年</a>。</p><p> Manics 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-manic-street-preachers-and-suede-played-as-they-kicked-off-their-co-headline-uk-tour-3770172">与 Suede 完成了英国联合巡演</a>，并已确定将在一月份在日本举行的 Rockin&#39; On Sonic 音乐节上与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pulp">Pulp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/weezer">Weezer</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/primal-scream">Primal Scream</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulps-first-gig-of-2025-confirmed-with-manic-street-preachers-weezer-primal-scream-3784018">演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-manic-street-preachers-triumphant-new-single-decline-fall-3788823">聆听 Manic Street Preachers 的胜利新单曲《Decline &amp; Fall》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
